        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Suit up. Preheat Oven.</p>
        <p>Welcome to Ironman Recipes, the kitchen laboratory where we believe that cooking isn't just a chore—it's a superpower.</p>
        <p>We started this site with a simple philosophy: you don't need a high-tech suit to be a hero in the kitchen, but you do need the right tools and the right blueprint. Like Tony Stark in his workshop, we are obsessed with tinkering, testing, and upgrading. We take classic recipes and give them a "Mark II" upgrade—streamlined techniques, bold flavor profiles, and a little bit of flair.</p>
        <p>Whether you're facing a 5-minute breakfast scramble (your "Emergency Protocol") or preparing a gourmet dinner that requires absolute precision (your "Maximum Power" mode), we've got your back.</p>
        <p>Here, failure isn't an option; it's just a prototype. We burn the toast so you don't have to. We've tested the theory so you can execute the practice. Because at the end of the day, the greatest weapon you have isn't a repulsor ray—it's a whisk.</p>
        <p>So, suit up. Grab your pan. And let's cook like we've got something to prove.</p>
